<h2>seg: Measuring Spatial Segregation</h2>
<p>Measuring spatial segregation. The methods implemented in this 
        package include White's P index (1983) &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1086%2F227768">doi:10.1086/227768</a>&gt;, 
        Morrill's D(adj) (1991), Wong's D(w) and D(s) (1993) 
        &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1080%2F00420989320080551">doi:10.1080/00420989320080551</a>&gt;, and Reardon and O'Sullivan's set of 
        spatial segregation measures (2004) 
        &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.0081-1750.2004.00150.x">doi:10.1111/j.0081-1750.2004.00150.x</a>&gt;.</p>
